title: Cooking Poultry with the Steam Wall Oven | Jenn-Air
description:
See how to get amazing results when cooking poultry in a Steam and Convection Wall Oven with Chef Ann Nolan.

The Jenn-Air® Steam and Convection Wall Oven yields consistent cooking results with heat that's evenly distributed throughout the oven. Chef Ann Nolan, the Culinary Training Chef for Jenn-Air, demonstrates how steam and convection together can help to achieve a roasted duck that’s tender inside and crisped outside.
